dct_description_sm: The Farm Journal map of Burlington County, New Jersey. County and each township are outlined in green. Roads in each township are numbered to correspond with the Farm Journal Farm Directory of the County. Railroads and electric lines are also indicated.
Some discoloration and tearing at some folds.
